title: FRANCE BURNS AGAIN! What The F*CK Is Going On?
description:
It’s Independence Day – a day to celebrate patriotism. But while in France the murder of a 17-year-old sparks a revolt that continues for a seventh night against a militarised expanded police force, the US continues to approve arm sales to Ukraine and Taiwan. So, are we at a point where killing and being killed is now the highest form of patriotism? #france #4july #independenceday
